<P>THE DRAMATIST, A COMEDY, IN FIVE ACTS.</P>
<P>WRITTEN BY &mdash;REYNOLDS, <ABBR>E&s;q</ABBR> <HI>Author of WERTER,</HI> &amp;c. AS PERFORMED AT THE <HI>THEATRE ROYAL SMOKE-ALLEY.</HI></P>
